Tang Yuet Ching is dedicated to crafting compelling digital narratives through the showcase of three captivating art pieces. As an artist, I aim to merge creativity with technology, offering a unique and immersive experience for viewers. Dive into my world of imagination and discover the stories behind each creation.

Dessert product design
I created a piece for Lifetastic's signature Strawberry Watermelon Cake, aiming to convey its refreshing and sweet essence. This work utilized various methods, including photography and painting, featuring models, product shots, posters, and even a comic.

